
---


@startuml

' Define classes and their attributes

class User {
    +String firstName
    +String lastName
    +String email (username)
    +String password
    +String postalAddress
    +String phoneNumber
}

class Organizer {
    +createEvent()
    +inviteAttendee()
    +updateChecklist()
    +viewEventStatus()
    +addTaskToGlobalChecklist()
}

class Attendee {
    +respondToInvitation()
    +selectTasks()
}

class Event {
    +String type
    +DateTime startDate
    +DateTime endDate
    +String occasion
    +Location location
    +List<Organizer> organizers
    +List<Attendee> attendees
    +Checklist checklist
}

class Checklist {
    +List<Task> tasks
}

class Task {
    +String description
    +TaskStatus status
    +boolean assignedToAttendee
    +Attendee? assignee
}

enum TaskStatus {
    NeedsToBeDone
    Done
    NotApplicable
}

class Location {
    +String name
    +String address
}

class Invitation {
    +Attendee attendee
    +Event event
    +ResponseStatus responseStatus
}

enum ResponseStatus {
    Attending
    Maybe
    NotAttending
    NoResponse
}

' Inheritance relationships
User <|-- Organizer
User <|-- Attendee

' Associations
Organizer "1..*" -- "1" Event : organizes
Event "1" -- "1..*" Checklist : has
Event "1" -- "0..*" Attendee : invites
Event "1" -- "1..*" Location : takes place at
Checklist "1" -- "1..*" Task : contains
Task "0..1" -- "1" Attendee : assigned to
Attendee "1" -- "1" Invitation : receives
Event "1" -- "1" Invitation : sends

@enduml

---

### 📌 Explanation of Key Relationships:

- **User** is an abstract class, with **Organizer** and **Attendee** as its subclasses.
- An **Event** can be organized by one or more **Organizers**, and can invite multiple **Attendees**.
- Each **Event** has a **Checklist**, which includes various **Tasks**.
- A **Task** may be assigned to an **Attendee**, if required.
- **Attendees** receive **Invitations**, which have a **ResponseStatus**.
- **Locations** can be reused across events.

